## Limitations
This report is limited by the availability of recent data and the potential bias in sources advocating against marijuana legalization. Additionally, the rapidly changing legal landscape and emerging research may alter the current understanding of marijuana's impacts. Further studies are needed to provide a more comprehensive view of the long-term effects of marijuana use and legalization.

